added.title: A Wide Delivery
added.description: When the trains must deliver in pairs, Thomas is disappointed to be paired with Diesel instead of his BFF Percy.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Counting Cows
added.description: When Thomas and Percy volunteer to deliver a herd of cows, they realize that the cows keep wandering off on their own adventures unless the two friends can both pay better attention.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: If It's Broke, Fix It
added.description: Dibble helps Grumpy work on his latest invention, a device to stop Bluster's bad vibe plow. Dibble's endless high spirits and sense of fun wear on Grumpy, until he finally says she can't work with him anymore. It's only later that Grumpy understands he needs Dibble's free-spirit inventiveness and creative energy.

added.title: Birthday Present/Gilbert/Summer Goodnight/Scared of Dogs/The Zoo
added.description: It's Caillou's birthday and he's having a little party./Caillou has nobody to play with./Caillou just can't get to sleep./Caillou is scared by a stranger's dog./Caillou and his family go to the zoo.

added.title: The Staff of Wisdom
added.description: Mush-Mush is amazed by the way Mushpot uses his staff of wisdom and how awesome it makes him look. Mush-Mush wants to be as cool as Mushpot and asks him to lend him his staff of wisdom. But the staff comes with a lot of responsibilities.

added.title: Voo Voo
added.description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

added.title: Hush
added.description: Pocoyo and his gang want to make friends with a butterfly but every time they say hello, it flies away. With Sleepy Bird's help, they realize how to get close to the butterfly.

added.title: I'm Taking You In
added.description: When Arlo's mom goes out hunting for food, Lucas decides to look after Arlo for the night. How hard can it be to look after a little Owl?

added.title: The Grumpy Effect
added.description: Bluster traps Grumpy in a frustration-inducing labyrinth in an attempt to capture his grumpiness and turn it into the ultimate Bad Seed, which when planted will create new areas of Blusterland. The scheme backfires when Bluster refuses to listen to the warnings of his underlings, and Grumpy's inner kindness turns the Bad Seed into a force for good.

added.title: New Babysitter/Theme Park/School Bus/Sleeps Over/Hurts Himself
added.description: Mom and Dad are going out./Caillou and his family go to a theme park./Caillou doesn't go to school./It's the first time Caillou is going to spend the night away from his home./Poor Caillou! He's fallen off his bike and scraped his knee.

added.title: The Hero Trap
added.description: The Mushlets love Mush-Mush's heroic stories. But when they demand to see him actually do something heroic, Mush-Mush feels he can't back out - and so ends up stuck up a cliff. Relieved to be rescued by Chep and Lilit, Mush-Mush is about to admit that he isn't a hero when the Mushlets find themselves in danger. Now Mush-Mush has no choice but to be a real hero!

added.title: Here I Go
added.description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

added.title: Double Bubble
added.description: Pocoyo is enjoying blowing bubbles with his bubble maker. Elly wants to play too. They can't agree on who gets to play with it. Finally they realize that the best way to play is to share.

added.title: Something Up There
added.description: After hearing a horrible screech from the fireplace, Lucas is nominated by his friends to go up and find out what is causing the noise.

added.title: Takers Keepers
added.description: Daffy steals Taz's favorite toy but he learns you can't just take everything you want.

added.title: To Tell the Tooth
added.description: When Bugs loses a baby tooth, Daffy tries to figure out how to scam the tooth fairy.

added.title: Race for the Sodor Cup
added.description: Super-fast Kana is convinced that her speed is all she needs to win the world renowned Race for the Sodor Cup. However, when she ends up paired with Thomas for the games, she discovers that it takes much more than speed to really be a champion.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

removed.description: When Findley sees a documentary about spiders being the natural predator of the fly, he decides that maybe Lucas isn't the big friend he thought he was! The more Findley tries to get away from Lucas, the more Lucas thinks this is a great game.
